Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah! No, Ebina, I was just thinking,}Ah! Mình chỉ đang nghĩ là muốn có anh trai như vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'd like a brother like that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Y-yeah. }Ư-Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Really, that's all!}Thật đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Y-yeah!}Ư-Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have to go to the principal's office,}Mình phải đến phòng hiệu trưởng,\N nên các cậu cứ về trước đi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{so you all go on ahead.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Very well!}Mình biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay. See you later, Umaru. }Ừm. Mai gặp nhé, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{U-until tomorrow. }H-Hẹn mai gặp lại.
