Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Taihei Doma sure was something else. }Doma Taihei cũng rất giỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Taihei the Demon," they called him. }"Quỷ dữ Taihei", đó là cách mọi người gọi em ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Takes you back, doesn't it? He was an excellent student.}Hoài niệm nhỉ? Em ấy là học sinh rất giỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your brother is amazing!}Onii-san ấn tượng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I like Umaru's brother, indeed!}Mình thích Onii-san rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{And makes you feel at ease somehow.  }Anh ấy giúp mình cảm thấy yên tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{He was an excellent student.}Em ấy là học sinh rất giỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Big Brother!}Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Looks like he's just come back from shopping. }Có vẻ anh ấy vừa đi mua đồ về.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I know! I'll scare him from behind!}Biết rồi! Hãy làm anh ấy giật mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is sure to give him a shock!}Cái này sẽ làm anh ấy bất ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Here goes!}Được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Biiig Brothe-!}Onii-cha...
