Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ham! Ham! Ah, ham, ham, ham-ham!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugi wa kime-pose. Saa, ikimasu wa yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next up, my signature pose. Here I go, indeed!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbafeen! Shbafeen! Shba-shbafeen!
